    "body": "There is a `disabled` attribute on the button when the results are exhausted. If you want to delete it, you can do it with css: \r\n\r\n```css\r\n.ais-infinite-hits--showmoreButton:disabled {\r\n  display: none;\r\n}\r\n```",
